  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Probable Alzheimer's disease according to the NINCDS-ADRDA (National Institute of
             Neurological and Communicative Disorders and Stroke and the Alzheimer's Disease and
             Related Disorders Association) and DSM-IV (Diagnostic and Statistical Manual of Mental
             Disorders) criteria;

          -  MMSE score of ≥10 and ≤ 26;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Bradycardia (beats per minute less than 50)

          -  Body weight less than 40 kg;

          -  Hypersensitivity to cholinesterase inhibitors.

        Other protocol-defined inclusion/exclusion criteria may apply
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
